manifests.contents:
[[bin]]
path = "collector_service/src/main.rs"
name = "collector_service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[[bin]]
path = "monitor_service/src/main.rs"
name = "monitor_service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[[bin]]
path = "writer_service/src/main.rs"
name = "writer_service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[package]
name = "collector"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4.4.0"
config = "0.11"
dotenv = "0.15"
futures = "0.3.31"
lapin = "2.0"
rand = "0.9.0"
serde_derive = "1.0"
serde_json = "1.0.138"
slog = "2.7"
slog-async = "2.7"
slog-envlogger = "2.0"
slog-term = "2.9"
thiserror = "2.0.11"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3.19"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.entity]
path = "entity"

[dependencies.migration]
path = "migration"

[dependencies.redis]
version = "0.29.0"
features = ["tokio-comp"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.12"
features = ["json", "cookies", "http2", "rustls-tls", "socks"]

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "1.1.5"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "sqlx-postgres", "with-chrono", "with-json"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "=0.6.3"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "postgres", "chrono"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.43.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tokio-tungstenite]
version = "0.26.1"
features = ["native-tls"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.7.0"
features = ["v4"]

[lib]
path = "common/src/lib.rs"
name = "common"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "entity"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "1.1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.212"
features = ["derive"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "entity"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "migration"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "migration"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
publish = false

[dependencies.async-std]
version = "1"
features = ["attributes", "tokio1"]

[dependencies.sea-orm-migration]
version = "1.1.0"
features = ["runtime-tokio-native-tls", "sqlx-postgres", "with-chrono", "with-json", "cli"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "migration"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]
